PrecisOrder directing that Quit-Claim Letters Patent do issue to DUVO CONSTRUCTION LTÉE granting unto them all rights or privileges of the Crown with respect to a parcel of land (4,030 m²) situated at 4077-4097 de la Seine Street, in the City of Laval, Quebec, together with the 72 residential condominium units erected thereon, all of which was acquired by the Crown in 1980 upon the dissolution of Corporation Équipements à Pneus Magnum Ltée under the Canada Business Corporations Act.
